Text: "Hi,\nFirst I'm introduced to myself.\nMy name is Ravi and I'm from India, Gujarat.\n\
  I love traveling and i think all the people's last wish is the same. \U0001F604\
  \ But sometimes they failed.\n\nI have business of Export so, I'm traveling minimum\
  \ 3 country every year.\nWhenever i travel then one of the my best friend cum my\
  \ business partner is always with me.\n\nWhenever we travel, we will do the travel\
  \ expenses in chipest rate (all the things like airfare, Accommodation, food and\
  \ all).\nSo, The one who enjoyed living and is not anywhere.\n\nThis year i visited\
  \ 3  country one is UAE - Dubai, second is China - Zhengzhou and third is Thailand\
  \ - Pattaya.\n\nLast i visited Pattaya City and it's experience is really amazing.\n\
  We do business as well as entertainment and its combination is awesome.\nI love\
  \ meet a new people and know more about his country and that people."
